 Four formlessnesses There is the case friends where a monkwith the complete transcending of perceptions of form with the disappearance of perceptions of resistance and not attending to perceptions of multiplicity Infinite spaceenters  remains in the dimension of the infinitude of space
With the complete transcending of the dimension of the infinitude of space Infinite consciousness he enters  remains in the dimension of the infinitude of consciousness
With the complete transcending of the dimension of the infinitude of consciousness There is nothing he enters  remains in the dimension of nothingness
