Yes lord we fear pain We dislike pain
Then on realizing the significance of that the Blessed One on that occasion exclaimed
If you fear pain if you dislike pain
dont anywhere do an evil deed in open or in secret
If youre doing or will do an evil deed
you wont escape pain catching up as you run away
I have heard that on one occasion the Blessed One was staying near Sāvatthī at Jetas Grove Anāthapiṇḍikas monastery
