Monks there is the case where a certain person is corruptminded Having encompassed that mind with my awareness I discern If this person were to die at this instant then as if he were to be carried off he would thus be placed in hell
Why is that
Because his mind is corrupt
Its because of corruptmindedness that there are cases where beingsat the breakup of the body after deathreappear in a plane of deprivation a bad destination a lower realm hell
This is the meaning of what the Blessed One said
So with regard to this it was said
