Sariputta having established the brahmin Dhananjani in the inferior Brahmaworld why did you rise from your seat and leave while there was still more to be done
Venerable sir I thought thus These brahmins are devoted to the Brahmaworld Suppose I show the brahmin Dhananjani the path to the company of Brahma
Sariputta the brahmin Dhananjani has died and has reappeared in the Brahmaworld
and the venerable Sariputta asked him Is the Blessed One well and strong friend
and there he lived in the Bamboo Grove the Squirrels Sanctuary
