And who is that
There is brahmin a town to the east called Savatthi
There the Blessed One the Arahant the Perfectly Enlightened One is now dwelling
The Blessed One has overcome this adherence to lust for sensual pleasures bondage to it fixation on itobsession by it holding firmly to it and he has overcome this adherence to lust for views bondage to it fixation on it obsession by it holding firmly to it
