Indeed that Blessed One has overcome this adherence to lust for sensual pleasures bondage to it fixation on it obsession by it holding firmly to it and he has overcome this adherence to lust for views bondage to it fixation on it obsession by it holding firmly to it
Excellent Master Kaccana Excellent Master Kaccana
Master Kaccana has made the Dhamma clear in many ways as though he were turning up right what had been overthrown revealing what was hidden showing the way to one who was lost or holding up a lamp in the darkness so those with good eyesight can see forms
