Here theres no taming for one fond of conceit
no sagacity for one unconcentrated
One dwelling alone in the wilderness heedlessly
wont cross over beyond Deaths realm
his mind wellconcentrated wellaware everywhere released
The Buddha Abandoning conceit
one dwelling alone in the wilderness heedfully
He will cross over beyond Deaths realm
Near Sāvatthī
