Here is a brief demonstration
A All Suffering meets together under seven terms
All Suffering can be demonstrated by the following terms  association with the loathed and dissociation from the loved 
It is also comprised by painfulness as pain painfulness in determinations and painfulness in change 
so this suffering is all comprised also by these three terms
B Herein all Origin is threefold without fourth without fifth
How threefold
Craving view and action
Herein while craving is the origin of being it is action
So any inferiority and superiority in the various kinds of being existence and destinations is  comprised by the three kinds of painfulness  and also the body with its consciousness belonging to one shut in by ignorance and fettered by craving for being  which body having been procured owing to the two roots craving and ignorance is comprised by the three painfulnesses too
Likewise view can be arrived at from perversion
That can be demonstrated as sevenfold 
Herein what is the single perverting
It is distorted apprehension way of entry by rejection of the fact such that it apprehends distortedly that there is permanence in the impermanent
While this perverting is one what is perverted is perception cognizance and view
What are the four objects of perversion
They are the body feeling cognizance and ideas
When someone goes by the perversions thus his unprofitable cognizance increases
Herein the perversion of perception increases the unprofitable root hate
Herein the fruit of the unprofitable root hate is the three wrongnesses namely wrong speech wrong action and wrong livelihood  the fruit of the unprofitable root greed is the three wrongnesses namely wrong intention wrong effort and wrong concentration  the fruit of the unprofitable root delusion is the two wrongnesses namely wrong view and wrong mindfulness
Thus this unprofitable cognizance has cause and has condition  the perversions are the condition and the unprofitable roots are the cause  And these same perversion and root in their opposite neither less nor more can be demonstrated as the two conditions 
in the case of C Cessation and in the case of D the Path but the conditions are four  as well by assuming perversion in the opposite
