What must be abandoned has been abandoned Therefore brahmin I am a Buddha
For welfare in this very life And happiness in lives to come
Since leave is given you please ask Whatever you aspire to know
and others too ask me about good in this life
How does one become a brahmin And how does one attain to knowledge
