Impermanent What is impermanent
The five aggregates are impermanent
In what sense impermanent
Impermanent in the sense of rise and fall
How many characteristics does he see who sees the rise of the five aggregates How many characteristics does he see who sees the fall of the five aggregates How many characteristics does he see who sees the rise and fall of thefive aggregates
He who sees the rise of the five aggregates sees twentyfive characteristics He who sees the fall of the five aggregates sees twentyfive characteristics
He who sees the rise and fall of the five aggregates sees fifty characteristics
