Through inbreaths and outbreaths contemplating impermanence there are ideas The establishment is mindfulness The contemplation is knowledge
Ideas are the establishment  but they are not the mindfulness Mindfulness is both the establishment and the mindfulness
By means of that knowledge and that mindfulness he contemplates those ideas
Hence Development of the Foundation of Mindfulness consisting in contemplation of ideas as ideas is said
He contemplates
Seeing danger in materiality he has zeal for the fading away of greed for materiality he is resolute in faith and his cognizance is well steadied thereon
