Bhikkhus when the deliverance of will by lovingkindness is cultivated developed and made much of made the vehicle made the foundation established consolidated and properly undertaken then eleven blessings can be expected
What eleven
A man sleeps in comfort wakes in comfort and dreams no evil dreams he is dear to human beings he is dear to nonhuman beings deities guard him fire and poison do not harm him his mind is easily concentrated the expression on his face is serene he dies undeluded and if he does not penetrate the supreme state he will be reborn in the Brahmā world
When the deliverance of will by lovingkindness is cultivated developed and made much of made the vehicle made the foundation established consolidated and properly undertaken then these eleven blessings can be expected 
 May all breathing things in the eastern direction   May all in the eastern direction who are   May all persons in the eastern direction   May all who have a personality in the eastern direction   May all women in the eastern direction   May all men in the eastern direction  May all Noble Ones in the eastern direction  May all who are not Noble Ones in the eastern direction  May all deities in the eastern direction  May all human beings in the eastern direction   May all in the states of deprivation in the eastern direction
May all beings in the western direction May all beings in the northern direction May all beings in the southern direction  May all beings in the eastern intermediate direction May all beings in the western intermediate direction May all beings in the northern intermediate direction  May all beings in the southern intermediate direction  May all beings in the lower direction  May all beings in the upper direction be free from enmity distress and affliction and may they live happily
May all beings in the eastern direction be free from enmity distress and affliction and may they live happily
